::FZ::

"Take the fastest vehicle in the Iron Fist and scout out.." he 
pauses, his mind going over the locations to be scouted. It briefly 
accesses the Iron Fist's datatracks for recent scanner results. "The 
Predacon base. Bloodystrike has gotten held up there, so if you can 
find him, tell him to return to base. We are on friendly terms with 
the Predacons, so they shouldn't fire on you. Report whenever you 
can."

Squizzy's transmission is recieved by both FZ and Zardus, FZ 
replying. "I'll be right there, Squizzy."

He walks off into the Iron Fist, heading for the labs.
